snippet: Venus Williams and Sloane Stephens will lead the U.S. Fed Cup team against Poland next month — but Williams' sister Serena is not on the roster....
lead_paragraph: Venus Williams and Sloane Stephens will lead the U.S. Fed Cup team against Poland next month — but Williams' sister Serena is not on the roster.
